WEBVTT

00:00.282 --> 00:01.389
I work at a bookshop.

00:02.283 --> 00:05.025
It's in a busy location with a lot of old buildings.

00:05.634 --> 00:09.536
It's a small space, but many people come to look for their favorite books.

00:11.091 --> 00:13.373
My office is in a quiet part of our town.

00:13.753 --> 00:16.644
It only has two floors, but it has big windows.

00:17.654 --> 00:19.673
There is a big open space outside.

00:20.447 --> 00:23.817
We can park our cars there or do some outdoor activities.

